{"tid":1961754,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"紀錄歷史 抗議封網 京百人紋「404」上身","createTime":"2020-04-07T04:07:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T04:52:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"94a848875edab297669893a871e3f397683c58be","tid":1961754,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T04:07:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200407/3353SEBLQ6DBTZPNPKBWXXVDNY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200407%2F3353SEBLQ6DBTZPNPKBWXXVDNY%2F&d=oVNa%2F3rGcR5VJv77DJ2le1DHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=ee8c75b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200407%2F3353SEBLQ6DBTZPNPKBWXXVDNY%2F&h=ff23c45f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200407/3353SEBLQ6DBTZPNPKBWXXVDNY/</a><br />\n<br />\n紀錄歷史 抗議封網<br />\n京百人紋「404」上身<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200407/large/1586188741_4170.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200407%2Flarge%2F1586188741_4170.gif&h=86c381ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n北京女紋身師劉安之。<br />\n<br />\n習近平上台後視互聯網為「大敵」，網管日益嚴厲，動輒封網刪文，令內地網民時常遭遇「404」（即網頁或內容被刪除後，網絡的自動顯示）。北京一群紋身愛好者近期發起「404NotFound紋身計劃」，參與者可免費獲紋身師為其紋上「404NotFound」字樣，以另類方式對當局網管表達不滿。發起者透露目前已有近百人參加；並否認此活動涉政治。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200407/large/1586188741_5f3f.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200407%2Flarge%2F1586188741_5f3f.gif&h=d2206811&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n編號58希望「404NotFound」這個紋身讓每個微小個體都能不畏強權。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200407/large/1586188742_c700.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200407%2Flarge%2F1586188742_c700.gif&h=03f3384a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n編號86將「404NotFound」紋在手臂，希望未來不會迷失。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「提醒自己保持憤怒」<br />\n<br />\n該活動發起人是北京80後女紋身師劉安之。劉近日接受內地自媒體TATYOU採訪表示，該計劃「無關政治，只關乎存在和歷史」。參與者只要回答兩個問題「你是誰」、「你為甚麼在乎」，就可獲劉親自為其紋上字號和款式一樣的「404NotFound」一行字；唯一不同是末尾四位數編號，按紋身完成先後排序。劉安之是0000號，最近一位參與者是0094號；即至今已有95人參與該活動。<br />\n<br />\n劉安之表示，把「404NotFound」這個概念放在生活上，「我們不想諷刺甚麼，就是想要，用身體去接受它。」劉向記者展示參與者對她兩個問題的回應，其中0007號表示，參與活動「是對自己的提醒。保持批判與質疑。靈魂不可被噤聲。」0050號則寫道：「為了提醒自己保持憤怒，即使這只能是一種情緒。」0060號表示：「選擇用我的皮膚去記錄，是我的發聲方式，對歷史的見證。」<br />\n<br />\n被問到此紋身計劃是否行為藝術，劉安之稱「是行為。藝術不藝術，就由別人說吧」。據了解，內地越來越多年輕人喜歡紋身，特別是一些女性，喜歡在隱閉部位紋花草等，以討情侶喜歡；僅北京就有紋身店幾百家；但紋身目前仍未被主流社會接納，官方招公務員、軍方徵兵等，仍視紋身者為異類，拒之門外。本報昨日未能聯絡上劉安之回應。<br />\n<br />\n中國數字時代網"},{"pid":"88de2385f1e4395c485bbf0a53531d9943302f79","tid":1961754,"uid":69221,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T04:08:57.000Z","msg":"第8964個會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"957c546e7c292fd903b9a9361e932905156e25e3","tid":1961754,"uid":3270,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"88de2385f1e4395c485bbf0a53531d9943302f79","tid":1961754,"uid":69221,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T04:08:57.000Z","msg":"第8964個會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T04:10:04.000Z","msg":"本身呢個數就係not found <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"619b2454e3b76667150843d2aff15b7d97a30577","tid":1961754,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88de2385f1e4395c485bbf0a53531d9943302f79","tid":1961754,"uid":69221,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T04:08:57.000Z","msg":"第8964個會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T04:10:35.000Z","msg":"被消失"},{"pid":"94e5d1a6d462bf9a41f7b3835e0bdc24d716ed67","tid":1961754,"uid":288707,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T04:10:36.000Z","msg":"行為藝術，畫面好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a77c0c51586384a3959092a07041a13bff3812e","tid":1961754,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T04:12:43.000Z","msg":"真勇者，同以前中國d罪犯比人紋係罪犯一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c0113683a20e0c2a788635150d7b1464b7bdb0f","tid":1961754,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a77c0c51586384a3959092a07041a13bff3812e","tid":1961754,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T04:12:43.000Z","msg":"真勇者，同以前中國d罪犯比人紋係罪犯一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T04:52:21.000Z","msg":"大鳴大放<br />\n畀你heat下先<br />\n差唔多就收網"}]}